			<p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:2;11:26" xtrf="file:/Users/waybri01/gitrepos/dita-glossary-authoring-and-publishing/w_glossary/SampleBook/arm1/ggb1473691529883.xml">Hardware management of the Access flag is enabled by the following configuration
				fields:</p>
			<ul class="- topic/ul " xtrc="ul:1;13:28" xtrf="file:/Users/waybri01/gitrepos/dita-glossary-authoring-and-publishing/w_glossary/SampleBook/arm1/ggb1473691529883.xml">
