				<li class="- topic/li " xtrc="li:2;15:29" xtrf="file:/Users/waybri01/gitrepos/dita-glossary-authoring-and-publishing/w_glossary/SampleBook/arm1/ggb1473691529883.xml">VTCR_EL2.HA for stage 2 translations.</li>
			</ul>
			<p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:3;17:26" xtrf="file:/Users/waybri01/gitrepos/dita-glossary-authoring-and-publishing/w_glossary/SampleBook/arm1/ggb1473691529883.xml">Hardware management of <term class="- topic/term " keyref="dirty" xtrc="term:1;17:70" xtrf="file:/Users/waybri01/gitrepos/dita-glossary-authoring-and-publishing/w_glossary/SampleBook/arm1/ggb1473691529883.xml">dirty</term> state is enabled by the following configuration fields:</p>
			<ul class="- topic/ul " xtrc="ul:2;18:28" xtrf="file:/Users/waybri01/gitrepos/dita-glossary-authoring-and-publishing/w_glossary/SampleBook/arm1/ggb1473691529883.xml">
