				<li class="- topic/li " xtrc="li:4;20:29" xtrf="file:/Users/waybri01/gitrepos/dita-glossary-authoring-and-publishing/w_glossary/SampleBook/arm1/ggb1473691529883.xml">VTCR_EL2.HD for stage 2 translations.</li>
			</ul>
			<note class="- topic/note " xtrc="note:1;22:32" xtrf="file:/Users/waybri01/gitrepos/dita-glossary-authoring-and-publishing/w_glossary/SampleBook/arm1/ggb1473691529883.xml">Hardware management of  state can only be enabled if hardware management of the Access
				flag is enabled.</note>
