			<p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:5;26:26" xtrf="file:/Users/waybri01/gitrepos/dita-glossary-authoring-and-publishing/w_glossary/SampleBook/arm1/ggb1473691529883.xml">The <term class="- topic/term " keyref="core" xtrc="term:3;26:50" xtrf="file:/Users/waybri01/gitrepos/dita-glossary-authoring-and-publishing/w_glossary/SampleBook/arm1/ggb1473691529883.xml">core</term> supports hardware update only in outer <term class="- topic/term " keyref="write" xtrc="term:4;26:122" xtrf="file:/Users/waybri01/gitrepos/dita-glossary-authoring-and-publishing/w_glossary/SampleBook/arm1/ggb1473691529883.xml">Write</term>-Back and inner
